<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bored-adj">bored <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɔːrd/    美 /bɔːd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>厌烦的；厌倦的；烦闷的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There was a bored expression on her face. 
她脸上有一种厌倦的表情。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-get-bored-with">(be / get) bored with</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…感到厌倦 (be fed up with)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Bored with life in the city, he moved to a remote village.
因为厌倦了城市的生活，他搬到了一个偏远的村庄。</p><footer>译林 ⑦-1</footer></div></div>